{"data":[{"date":"15:32 12/07","title":"Sao 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00f3i g\u00ec ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Barca?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/arthur-phat-bieu-ngay-gia-nhap-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb7c \u00e2n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arthur gia nh\u1eadp Barca</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur t\u1eeb Gremio. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Brazil qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2017/18 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00f3n anh. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arthur, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed ph\u00e1t sinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArthur \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Brazil. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ban b\u1eadt m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/arthur-phat-bieu-ngay-gia-nhap-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Arthur ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp Barca v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nT\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Arthur \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m. Trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng Gremio gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Copa Libertadores b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf&rdquo;, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Barca TV.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y vinh d\u1ef1.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang ra Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Arthur ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i cho Gremio trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Paulinho (tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u H\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1ea1i) \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang-180-190953.html\">Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/psg-chi-270-trieu-euro-mua-coutinho-180-190772.html\">C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c: PSG chi 270 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-paulinho-roi-barca-chi-sau-11-thang-180-190739.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Paulinho \u0111i th\u1eadt xa \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1... Trung Qu\u1ed1c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/neymar-muon-psg-rut-ruot-barca-180-190707.html\">Neymar mu\u1ed1n PSG r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/day-4-muc-tieu-sieu-khung-duoc-barca-nham-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-180-190595.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! 4 M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1185","checkdouble":"191037"},{"date":"15:22 12/07","title":"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</h2><h2>VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi 8 t\u1edbi, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng quy t\u1ee5 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m 'thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao' cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/giai-quoc-te-u-23-3_emlc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng U23 \u00dac. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do L\u0110B\u0110 \u00dac kh\u00f4ng thu x\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y n\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U19 tham d\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, BTC gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed9i Australia b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 t\u1eebng l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 U23 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1184","checkdouble":"191038"},{"date":"16:17 12/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a TBN: \"T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/9/tan-hlv-truong-cua-tbn-toi-se-khong-thay-doi-khien-nguoi-khac-hai-long.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-anh-463-190974.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia vs Anh </span>trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn sai v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Vida h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u00e0 Liverpool th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPhong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 sai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren tin Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Croatia. Lovren tin Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric phan phao truyen thong Anh sau khi DT Croatia gianh chien thang.\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau khi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Luka Modric\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Modric l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018. Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Modric ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Croatia n\u1eefa. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Modric kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1183","checkdouble":"191040"},{"date":"16:08 12/07","title":"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus nh\u0103m nhe th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/psg-va-juventus-muon-mua-brewster-sao-tre-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, sao tr\u1ebb 18 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi The Kop.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n sao tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRhian Brewster \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U17 World Cup di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2017. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, sao tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 2000 ghi t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn gi\u00fap U17 Anh gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrewster hi\u1ec7n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Liverpool. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi CLB n\u00e0y. Liverpool \u0111ang s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng m\u1edf c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/PSG-va-Juventus-muon-mua-Brewster-than-dong-cua-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brewster gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup U17</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u Brewster mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1. \u0110\u1ebfn nay, Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a ch\u00e0ng trai sinh t\u1ea1i London trong khi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o t\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus nh\u0103m nhe cu\u1ed7m Brewster</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Liverpool ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c sao tr\u1ebb \u1edf l\u1ea1i, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00ed \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o cho The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Brewster cua liverpool\" title=\"Brewster cua liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/psg-va-juventus-muon-mua-brewster-sao-tre-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Brewster</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u00ean, Brewster mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh song v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus sau khi c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u00f5i theo di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Brewster. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, Brewster \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Borussia Dortmund v\u00e0 RB Leipzig \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh. Ngo\u00e0i PSG v\u00e0 Juventus, c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng Arsenal, Tottenham, Barcelona v\u00e0 Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau d\u1ee5 Brewster v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish-172-190672.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir-172-190670.html\">Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-ky-chap-nhan-giai-cuu-shaqiri-neu-172-190604.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Shaqiri n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1182","checkdouble":"191041"},{"date":"15:58 12/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/del-pierro-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-chieu-mo-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Juventus, Alessandro Del Piero \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7.</h2><h2>Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Del Pierro l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Del-Pierro-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-Juventus-chieu-mo-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Juventus c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB&nbsp;Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Juve x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo sang Real kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 ngo\u00e0i 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 CR7, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 19 n\u0103m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi 'B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0', danh th\u1ee7 Alessandro Del Piero \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Juve, v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111ang n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Juve, v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u00fa h\u00ednh, khi\u1ebfn Serie A tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. T\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Juventus chi ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo l\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Anh ta lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng CLB m\u00e0 anh ta kho\u00e1c \u00e1o. Juventus \u0111ang c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean s\u00e2n ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Ronaldo&rdquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111ang l\u00e0 k\u1ebb b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1edbi 7 danh hi\u1ec7u Scudetto li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp trong 7 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua song Juve v\u1eabn \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Champions League. L\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 1995/96. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Bianconeri l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/10-ky-luc-co-the-bi-pha-khi-ronaldo-chuyen-sang-juventus-176-191027.html\">10 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 khi Ronaldo chuy\u1ec3n sang Juventus</span><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn CLB Juventus l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c \u0111ang ch\u1edd ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n chia ch\u00e1c khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Real Madrid n\u0103m 2009, nh\u01b0ng MU v\u1eabn thu v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n sau khi Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1181","checkdouble":"191043"},{"date":"16:45 12/07","title":"Lovren: \"M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-anh-463-190974.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia vs Anh </span>trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Croatia s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 Dejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/lovren-moi-nguoi-can-nhan-ra-chung-toi-la-nhung-nguoi-gioi-nhat.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn sai v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Dejan Lovren l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Vida h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDejan Lovren ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u00e0 Liverpool th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPhong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Liverpool v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 sai t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00ean nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lovren tin Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Luka Modric \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Croatia. Lovren tin Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric phan phao truyen thong Anh sau khi DT Croatia gianh chien thang.\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Anh sau khi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/luka-modric-phan-phao-truyen-thong-anh-sau-chien-thang-cua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lovren \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Luka Modric\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Modric l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018. Modric x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho danh hi\u1ec7u QBV 2018, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Modric ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Real v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Croatia n\u1eefa. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu Modric kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1180","checkdouble":"191045"},{"date":"16:43 12/07","title":"Chelsea b\u1ecb t\u00e2n binh NHA qua m\u1eb7t v\u1ee5 \u201cXavi ch\u00e2u Phi\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/giot-nuoc-mat-tre-tho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Chelsea m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Seri</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Jean-Michael Seri th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Nice. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng (ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68) nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSeri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;c\u1ee7a hi\u1ebfm&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u Phi. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/7 t\u1edbi v\u00e0 gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Xavi Hernandez c\u1ee7a Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Fulham-sap-mua-duoc-Jean-Michael-Seri-tu-Nice-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u00f9ng nh\u1eb1ng Conte v\u00e0 Sarri khi\u1ebfn Chelsea kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng qua, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Jean-Michael Seri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a sau c\u00f2n Arsenal chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n Lucas Torreira t\u1eeb Sampdoria. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n xao nh\u00e3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi Seri.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fulham s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri t\u1eeb Nice. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aston Villa \u1edf chung k\u1ebft play-off gi\u00fap Fulham \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Jean-Michael Seri\" title=\"tien ve Jean-Michael Seri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/giot-nuoc-mat-tre-tho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fulham s\u1eafp mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jean-Michael Seri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft thay m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eb1m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Seri, Fulham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Maxime Le Marchand c\u1ee7a anh t\u1ea1i Nice. Le Marchand c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trung v\u1ec7 l\u1eabn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Slavisa Jokanovic c\u00f3 th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua Seri, Fulham \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Aleksandar Mitrovic t\u1eeb Newcastle. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Serbia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Fulham m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 17 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Cottage c\u0169ng \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dedryck Boyata c\u1ee7a Celtic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819-172-187102.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fulham-len-hang-premier-league-201819-172-187102.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/19</span><br>\r\n<span>Fulham l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Premier League 2018/19 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Aston Villa \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft play-off tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tom Cairney \u0111\u00e3...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1179","checkdouble":"191047"},{"date":"16:30 12/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/hlv-park-hang-seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf trung v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea7m c\u01a1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c n\u00e0y, trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u V-League \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-co-nguy-co-mat-tro-cung-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi ASIAD 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 su\u1ea5t cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean lo l\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 'th\u00e9p' Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. T\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t 3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997, khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n trong 10 ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi th\u1eddi gian n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 23/7 t\u1edbi, ngay sau khi v\u00f2ng 20 V-League k\u1ebft th\u00fac. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/8 tr\u00ean SV\u0110 QG M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u1edbi 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-bat-ngo-loai-thang-tay-u23-uc-khoi-giai-tu-hung-168-191038.html\">VFF b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd lo\u1ea1i th\u1eb3ng tay U23 \u00dac kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng</span><br>\r\nL\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam song cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T U23 \u00dac \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018-292-190436.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1178","checkdouble":"191049"},{"date":"17:11 12/07","title":"\u201cBom t\u1ea5n\u201d 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/bom-tan-60-trieu-bang-riyad-mahrez-cua-man-city-khung-khiep-co-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City mua Riyad Mahrez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Man xanh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Mahrez \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf s\u00e2n Etihad.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m nay, ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00f2i t\u1edbi Man City l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Riyad Mahrez b\u1ecb Leicester \u0111\u00e0y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n. D\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\">\r\n            <h3><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Riyad Mahrez T\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u1ee7ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Riyad Mahrez T\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u1ee7ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/Man-City-mua-Riyad-Mahrez-Tan-binh-60-trieu-bang-khung-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mahrez c\u00f3 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf NHA m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Riyad Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 10 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh ra m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 39% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ee9 trung b\u00ecnh 128,4 ph\u00fat, Mahrez l\u1ea1i in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSo s\u00e1nh s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng + ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o (22) c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Man City cho th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, anh x\u1ebfp sau Sterling (29, 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o), Sane (25, 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 15 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o) v\u00e0 De Bruyne (24, 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 16 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean David Silva (20), v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva (10). Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Mahrez c\u00f2n cao h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gabriel Jesus (16).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester, Mahrez ra s\u00e2n 109 trong t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 114 tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u1edf Premier League, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 mi\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec5m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0 Mahrez, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man City s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Mahrez c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 2015/16 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 24 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf Premier League c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahrez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi. K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef th\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t gi\u00fap Mahrez d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 1 \u0111\u1ed1i 1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez co 290 lan qua nguoi thanh cong trong 3 mua giai vua qua o NHA\" title=\"Mahrez c\u00f3 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u1edf NHA\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/ma.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mahrez c\u00f3 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua \u1edf NHA</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a Mahrez trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leicester.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 290 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1eeb Opta, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Eden Hazard, Wilfried Zaha v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01a1n t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Man City.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Claude Puel c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Mahrez: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i l\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mahrez \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mahrez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Leicester, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u01a1i gi\u00fap Mahrez ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" title=\"tien ve Riyad Mahrez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/Riyad-Mahrez-toi-Arsenal-thay-vi-Man-City-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>S\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Riyad Mahrez s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho Pep \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m l\u1ec7ch ph\u1ea3i, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e1 &ldquo;s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o&rdquo; khi c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n Etihad, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Mahrez \u0111ang do Raheem Sterling \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sterling \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Sterling sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 Mahrez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n t\u00e2n binh 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Man xanh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Kevin de Bruyne ho\u1eb7c David Silva ch\u01a1i \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m Mahrez s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City, Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 anh h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, Mahrez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Etihad m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-mahrez-172-190895.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua Riyad Mahrez</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1177","checkdouble":"191050"},{"date":"17:48 12/07","title":"Ronaldo sang Juve: Qu\u00e2n domino tr\u00ean TTCN \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/ronaldo-sang-juve-quan-domino-tren-ttcn-da-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch n\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bom t\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2>T\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec1u 50 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/m\u00f9a, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 l\u1edbn. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Real Madrid &ndash; d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia tay Ronaldo trong \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1o gi\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Perez, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, v\u1eeba n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng theo tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ecfi mua Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe &ndash; nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 hai th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u00ec v\u1eady, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; trong th\u1eddi gian qua &ndash; Eden Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/rod.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t bom t\u1ea5n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nSau nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng chi ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n (k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Gareth Bale), Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i chu k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169. Cristiano Ronaldo cho h\u1ecd c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed7i CR7, Real \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay m\u00e1u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Luka Modric. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 Lazio \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Savic v\u00e0 Hazard ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp l\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;si\u00eau nh\u00e2n&rdquo; 2 trong 1, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb&hellip; Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Real bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh cho c\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u La Liga. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Neymar v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay l\u00e0 CR7, Los Blancos c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng bom t\u1ea5n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/CHINH-THUC-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb di\u1ec5n ra</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Qu\u00e2n domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Eden Hazard ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a chu\u1ed7i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng mang t\u00ean CR7. Chelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jorginho t\u1eeb tay Man City, v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri. Khi m\u1ed9t thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn, h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1ng ti\u1ec1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Juventus, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i thu chi v\u00ec lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. Con s\u1ed1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1edbt nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111em v\u1ec1 Emre Can v\u1edbi ph\u00ed CNTD, b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1edfng trong \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gonzalo Higuain \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Chelsea, trong khi Paulo Dybala c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Juve kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;nu\u00f4i&rdquo; c\u1ea3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1i t\u00ean t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Ronaldo. Ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef c\u1ea3 3, nh\u1eefng Mario Mandzukic v\u00e0 Alex Sandro s\u1ebd b\u1eadt b\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus Qu\u00e2n Domino \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man United &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Khi Chelsea, Man United v\u00e0 Man City (\u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Mahrez) mua s\u1eafm, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Liverpool c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u00ecn. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u0103m nay c\u1ee7a Premier League s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00e2n k\u00edch n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cris Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo-180-190984.html\">Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o sau khi chia tay Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain-176-191019.html\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Juventus chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i &ldquo;cu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu-172-191022.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: &ldquo;K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t&rdquo; Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thua-nuoc-duc-tha-cau-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-172-191026.html\">Liverpool th\u1eeba n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ee5c th\u1ea3 c\u00e2u v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1176","checkdouble":"191051"},{"date":"09:09 12/07","title":"\"\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dt-anh-van-thieu-mot-manh-ghep-de-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Chris Waddle c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh BBC cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</h2><h2>\u0110T Anh thua \u0111\u1eafng Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi Kieran Trippier c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng d\u1eady v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ivan Perisic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mandzukic s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Pickford \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Balkan.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/DT-Anh-that-bai-vi-thieu-mot-cau-thu-sang-tao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110T\u00a0Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Nga. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Chris Waddle c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh BBC Sport cho r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Euro 2020.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ba trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 khi \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Jordan Henderson c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Dele Alli b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i im ti\u1ebfng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. Raheem Sterling th\u00ec v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. B\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1175","checkdouble":"191014"},{"date":"09:31 12/07","title":"\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dt-anh-thua-croatia-vi-phai-mac-ao-dau-mau-trang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, thay v\u00ec m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng Tam S\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1966.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh thua v\u00ec \u00e1o tr\u1eafng?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Guardian t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1950, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn. Khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, Tam S\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh vao ban ket World Cup 2018 day thuyet phuc.\" title=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Fabio-Capello-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi m\u1eb7c s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1eeb n\u0103m 1950, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Euro v\u00e0 World Cup v\u1edbi 71 l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, 24 tr\u1eadn m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. T\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u1eefa hai m\u00e0u \u00e1o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 46% (11 tr\u1eadn) so v\u1edbi 39% khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng (28 tr\u1eadn). Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1996 c\u0169ng v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. T\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 thua khi \u0110T Anh m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 17% (4 tr\u1eadn), so v\u1edbi 39% khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng (28 tr\u1eadn).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u00e1o tr\u1eafng, 3 l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, \u0110T Anh to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia, hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f2n ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ba tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng, \u0110T Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9. Hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Tam S\u01b0 thua B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Croatia - th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 tan v\u1ee1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec sao \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ph\u00e2n chia nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o &quot;ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&quot; khi g\u1eb7p Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0u \u00e1o &quot;ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&quot; c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 caro \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng, s\u1eafc \u00e1o n\u00e0y tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecf).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh thua Croatia vi phai mac ao dau mau trang?\" title=\"\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/dt-anh-thua-croatia-vi-phai-mac-ao-dau-mau-trang.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0110T Croatia m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u khi g\u1eb7p Anh. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu thua 1-2 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-van-thieu-mot-manh-ghep-de-thanh-cong-469-191014.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ha-guc-anh-cau-thu-croatia-pose-anh-an-mung-465-191012.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia thi nhau pose \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng l\u00ean MXH</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mourinho-noi-ve-that-bai-tran-anh-vs-croatia-421-191011.html\">Mourinho an \u1ee7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau khi tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\">Sao Croatia: T\u01b0\u1edfng Anh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-bao-ve-kane-sau-man-tang-hinh-truoc-croatia-469-191009.html\">HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau-465-191008.html\">Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1174","checkdouble":"191015"},{"date":"09:30 12/07","title":"Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CalcioMercato ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus hy sinh Higuain</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o giao k\u00e8o g\u1eafn b\u00f3 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Gonzalo Higuain kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 trung phong s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 d\u1ecbch chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh sang m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CR7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 chuy\u00ean trang chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Calciomercato.com c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Juventus \u0111ang th\u1eeba th\u00e3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat gi\u1ecfi th\u00ec Chelsea l\u1ea1i \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Alvaro Morata h\u01a1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Chelsea d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh mua v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Higuain n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf Morata b\u1eb1ng Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn tin Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Juventus thanh l\u00fd trong c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin m\u1eebng v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o The Blues b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t ai l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Antonio Conte hay b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Chelsea tin HLV m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain. Conte hay Sarri \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Juventus s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 55 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-juventus-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-190942.html\">Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\">S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus-180-190910.html\">&ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1173","checkdouble":"191016"},{"date":"10:32 12/07","title":"\u0110\u00f2i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Croatia r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng.\r\n</h2><h2>Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t C\u0110V Tam S\u01b0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau 52 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh qu\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. H\u1ecd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng, khi \u0110T s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c ki\u1ec7t, ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 t\u1edbi C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh &ldquo;It&rsquo;s Coming Home &ndash; B\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi&rdquo;, c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef: &ldquo;T\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i, t\u00f4i y\u00eau n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng g\u1eedi t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u0103ng m\u1ea1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mbap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, \u0103n v\u1ea1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eeba, khi \u0111em kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;\u0111em b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Les Bleus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\">Sao Croatia: T\u01b0\u1edfng Anh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady!</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko l\u00ean m\u1eb7t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\">HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 khi \u0110T Anh qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1172","checkdouble":"191017"},{"date":"10:20 12/07","title":"Eric Dier n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/eric-dier-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dier th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Croatia t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec3u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V h\u00f4 h\u00e0o trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham &ndash; Eric Dier t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u00edt ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia\" title=\"Dier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/eric-dier-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf - ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nhau h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Ph\u00e1p 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc (k\u1ef3 EURO 2016), khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 theo c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i theo c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Dier ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, d\u00f9 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Jordan Henderson thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, \u0110T Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Football is NOT coming home!&rdquo; &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span><br>\r\nMarcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1171","checkdouble":"191018"}]}